lyrics:
[Verse]
Pack your bags, the journey begins
Adventure awaits, let your spirit sing
New sights to see, a world so wide
Our hearts on fire, let the wanderlust guide

[Chorus]
여행, 여행, let's go explore
여행, 여행, forever we'll soar
From mountains to oceans, we'll roam free
여행, 여행, this is where we're meant to be
